KMFDMDropThree26.name: KMFDM BRUTE Light C 26
description: The idea for LIGHT came about when I was looking for a way to
complete the trilogy of images from previous releases A Drug
Against War and Angst which featured the same vengeful female
assassin. The trilogy depicts an enraged and armed woman
shooting a man attempting to assault a woman who is ultimately
revealed to be the assassin's lover in the final image. LIGHT
was also my first attempt to draw in a cleaner, sharper style
using Adobe Illustrator for the background architectural
structures, elements I'd always struggled with. - BRUTE!
